Garner and Fuquay-Varina / Both Directions. Utility contractors for the Complete 540 project have scheduled temporary nightly road closures on U.S. 401 between Ten Ten Road and Ransdell Road. The nightly road closures will begin Monday January 25 at 11:00 P.M. for up to seven hours to reopen by 6 A.M. each morning. The nightly closures will occur from 11 P.M. to 6 A.M. each evening through Saturday January 30. Road closure and detour signs will be installed. There may also be intermittent shoulder closures on U.S. 401 to allow contractors to expedite the work.Access to Chandler Ridge Apartments as well as all other residences along U.S. 401 between Ten Ten Road and Ransdell Road will be maintained throughout the scheduled nightly closures.
